Long-time frenemies Hamisa Mobetto and Wema Sepetu have shown that they have reconciled. In an Instagram post, Sepetu wished Mobetto a happy birthday. "Happy Birthday Dogo langu. Happy Birthday to you sugar... Shine Bright like a Diamond. Basi hapo watu watasema," she wrote. Hamisa responded by writing, "Ahsante my Dada. Nawaseme tu jamani. I freaking love you." The two had been at odds after once dating the same man, Diamond Platnumz.